description: Who doesn't love a grilled cheese sandwich?! Bringing tasty, hot, fresh and fantastic grilled cheese sandwiches and amazing, made from scratch soups to you... in a rad truck! Using locally sourced products whenever possible and all the care your mom used plus some wacked out crazy combos, we have over a dozen variations on the classic you grew up with! Vegan? Gluten allergy? Lactose intolerant? We have you covered! We use local New England cheeses, fresh baked hometown bread, Daiya "cheese", gluten free bread, vegan mock meats, real all natural meats and fresh fruits and veggies, we have something for everyone!
name: Championship Melt
